                            p.footer-desc Similarly, a loan taken out to buy a car may be secured by the car. The duration of the loan.
                            form.subscribe(action="" autocomplete)
                                input.subscribe-email(type="email" placeholder="Enter your email")
                                button.subscribe-button(type="submit")
                                    img(srcSet="./images/arrow.png 2x", alt="icon-arrow-right")
                        .footer-column
                            h4.footer-heading Services
                            ul.footer-links
